The paper discusses a system for designing and debugging surveys, which involves aspects of human-computer interaction (cs.HC), natural language processing (cs.CL), cybernetics (cs.CY), computer engineering (cs.CE), and cryptography and security (cs.CR). However, the focus on survey design and analysis suggests that cs.HC is the most likely sub-category.
